    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>chicken breast strips</strong> into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong></p>",
