      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is cooking, chop your<strong> creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> and the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
