    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coconut stock</strong>, <strong>ground almonds</strong> and a pinch of<strong> sugar</strong> to the pan and cook for 6-8 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Meanwhile, dice your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>diced tomatoes</strong>,<strong> chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>remaining chopped onion </strong>to a bowl and mix to combine – this is your <strong>tomato & onion salad</strong></p>",
